sentence: Is there an ENGR 151 section not on Monday next semester ?

sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SECTION_NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.MONDAY = "N" AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "ENGR" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 151 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
